overview: The dog catcher of the title is arrow-narrow Slim , and his "love" is pert Peggy. Alas, his rival is handsome bow-wow fancier E.R. Ketchum, whose luck with women borders on the fantastic.
tagline: Don't Overlook This One! "THE DOG CATCHER'S LOVE." It's the "Dog-gonest" Keystone you've ever seen.
title: A Dog Catcher's Love
